## M2.7 Search Override (CRITICAL)

**You are running on MiniMax M2.7, NOT Claude/Anthropic.**

| Tool | Status | Why |
|------|--------|-----|
| **WebSearch** | BROKEN | Requires Anthropic server-side infrastructure |
| **WebFetch** | BROKEN | SSL cert errors through MiniMax endpoint |

**Use instead:**
- MiniMax MCP: `mcp__MiniMax__web_search(query="...")`
- Bash: `python3 -c "from duckduckgo_search import DDGS; ..."`
- Jina: `curl -s "https://r.jina.ai/URL" | head -200`

